<%- include('./include/header', {
title: 'CryptoDogs',
description: 'CryptoDogs',
keywords: 'CryptoDogs',
plugin: [],
private: ['../css/public.css'],
status: 'full',
login: false,
page: 'login'
}) %>

<main class="Main">
    <div class="Hero">
        <div class="Container Container--sm Container--center">
            <h2 class="Hero-h2">
                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                    <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                        讓我們開始吧...
                    </font>
                </font>
            </h2>
            <p class="Hero-description">
                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                    <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                        我們需要您的帳護的電子郵件地址。
                    </font>
                </font>
            </p>
            <form>
                <div class="Section">
                    <img class="ProfileHeader-image ProfileHeader-image--clickable" src="../images/profile/profile-17.png">
                </div>
                <div class="Section">
                    <p class="InputButtons-group">
                        <label for="address">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                    助記詞
                                </font>
                            </font>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" id="address" name="address" class="InputButtons InputButtons-input InputButtons--readonly" placeholder="Wallet Address" value="sgdadsfgsdfgsdfgsdf" maxlength="100" readonly="">
                    </p>
                    <p class="InputButtons-group">
                        <label for="email">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                    電郵
                                </font>
                            </font>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" id="email" name="email" class="InputButtons InputButtons-input" placeholder="e.g.: cryptodogs@cryptodogs.hk" value="cryptodogs@cryptodogs.hk" maxlength="100">
                    </p>
                    <p class="InputButtons-group">
                        <label for="nickname">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                    昵稱
                                </font>
                            </font>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" id="nickname" name="nickname" class="InputButtons InputButtons-input" placeholder="e.g.: cryptodogs" value="cryptodogs" maxlength="40">
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="Section">
                    <p>
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                如果您在登錄或編輯帳護時遇到問題，請發送郵件至
                            </font>
                            <a href="mailto:cryptodogs@cryptodogs.hk">
                                <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                    cryptodogs@cryptodogs.hk
                                </font>
                            </a>
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                。
                            </font>
                        </font>
                        <a href="mailto:meow@cryptokitties.co">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                            </font>
                        </a>
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                        </font>
                    </p>
                    <div class="Note Note--warning">
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                確保保存您的MetaMask登錄信息和帳護恢復詳細信息！
                            </font>
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                我們不能幫助您恢復訪問，如果妳失去它。
                            </font>
                        </font>
                    </div>
                    <button class="Button Button--love Button--larger">
                        <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                            <font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                                保存帳護信息
                            </font>
                        </font>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>


